<ul><li>Alt: <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFYaqut_ibn_&#39;Abd_Allah_al-Hamawi1861" class="citation book cs1 cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source"><a class="mw-selflink selflink">Yaqut ibn 'Abd Allah al-Hamawi</a> (1861). <a href="/wiki/Charles_Barbier_de_Meynard" title="Charles Barbier de Meynard">Charles Barbier de Meynard</a> (ed.). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_oD-9DTnKImAC"><i>Dictionnaire géographique, historique et littéraire de la Perse et des contrées adjacentes, extrait du "Mo'djem el-Bouldan" de Yaquout, et complété à l'aide de documents arabes et persans pour la plupart inédits</i></a> (in French and Arabic). <a href="/wiki/Paris" title="Paris">Paris</a>: <a href="/wiki/Imprimerie_nationale" class="mw-redirect" title="Imprimerie nationale">Impr. impériale</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Dictionnaire+g%C3%A9ographique%2C+historique+et+litt%C3%A9raire+de+la+Perse+et+des+contr%C3%A9es+adjacentes%2C+extrait+du+%22Mo%27djem+el-Bouldan%22+de+Yaquout%2C+et+compl%C3%A9t%C3%A9+%C3%A0+l%27aide+de+documents+arabes+et+persans+pour+la+plupart+in%C3%A9dits&amp;rft.place=Paris&amp;rft.pub=Impr.+imp%C3%A9riale&amp;rft.date=1861&amp;rft.au=Yaqut+ibn+%27Abd+Allah+al-Hamawi&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fbub_gb_oD-9DTnKImAC&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AYaqut+al-Hamawi" class="Z3988"></span></li></ul></li>
<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFJacut1866" class="citation book cs1 cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source"><a class="mw-selflink selflink">Jacut</a> (1866). <a href="/wiki/Ferdinand_W%C3%BCstenfeld" title="Ferdinand Wüstenfeld">Ferdinand Wüstenfeld</a> (ed.). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.70330"><i>Geographisches Wörterbuch</i></a> (in Arabic and German). Vol.&#160;1. <a href="/wiki/Leipzig" title="Leipzig">Leipzig</a>: <a href="/wiki/F.A._Brockhaus_AG" class="mw-redirect" title="F.A. Brockhaus AG">F.A. Brockhaus</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Geographisches+W%C3%B6rterbuch&amp;rft.place=Leipzig&amp;rft.pub=F.A.+Brockhaus&amp;rft.date=1866&amp;rft.au=Jacut&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fin.ernet.dli.2015.70330&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AYaqut+al-Hamawi" class="Z3988"></span>  (alt. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/geographischesw01ytib"><b>1</b>.(1866) </a>); <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.70331"><b>2</b>.(1867)</a>; <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.70332"><b>3</b>.(1868)</a>; <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.70333"><b>4</b>.(1869)</a>; <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.70334"><b>5</b>.(1873)</a>; <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.70335"><b>6</b>.(1870)</a>.</li>
